import React from 'react'
import {HeroContainer,
    HeroLeftWrapper,
    HeroImageLeft,
    HeroTextLeft,
    HeroRightWrapper,
    Video1Bg,
    Video2Bg,
    HeroRightText,} from './HeroElements'

function HeroSection() {
    return (
        <>
         <HeroContainer>
             <HeroLeftWrapper>
                <HeroImageLeft>
                    <HeroTextLeft>
                    Quality Just for you
                    </HeroTextLeft>    
                </HeroImageLeft>
            </HeroLeftWrapper>
            <HeroRightWrapper>
                <Video1Bg></Video1Bg>
                <Video2Bg></Video2Bg>
                <HeroRightText></HeroRightText>
            </HeroRightWrapper>

         </HeroContainer>   
        </>
    )
}

export default HeroSection
